''See also [[Pan]], [[PAN]]''
==English==

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/pæn/}}

===Etymology 1 ===
From Old English

====Noun====
'''pan''', plural '''[[pans]]'''
# Flat [[implement]] used for cooking in the oven and [[fry]]ing or [[boil]]ing on top of the stove.
# A [[load]] of [[bread]].

